<http://human.owl#genid2786> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Glucagon Cell" .
<http://human.owl#genid2789> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A medium-sized round lymphocyte of B or T-cell lineage with prominent nucleoli.  It is an intermediate cell between the lymphoblast and the small, mature lymphocyte." .
