<http://human.owl#genid2031> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Hand Digit 2 Phalanx" .
<http://human.owl#genid6495> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Flat Bone" .
