<http://human.owl#genid2924> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Type II Pneumocyte" .
<http://human.owl#genid2923> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A pleomorphic cell of the pulmonary alveolar epithelium that secretes surfactant and is distinguished by abundant cytoplasm containing numerous lipid-rich multilamellar bodies." .
