<http://human.owl#genid3689> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Apex of the Prostate" .
<http://human.owl#genid3698> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Body Region" .
<http://human.owl#genid3695> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Hepatic Flexure" .
