<http://human.owl#genid2015> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Endocrine Pancreas Secretion" .
<http://human.owl#genid1411> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A white blood cell that is derived from a lymphocyte stem cell matured in the thymus and characterized by a CD8 marker on the surface and an antigen-specific Epstein Barr virus T cell receptor." .
<http://human.owl#genid2019> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Tunica Intima" .
<http://human.owl#genid2943> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Testicular Tissue" .
