<http://human.owl#genid2026> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Part of the functional area of the prostate that is above and in front of the transitional zone. The central zone comprises about 20-25% of the gland and is the location of about 10% of the prostate cancers found in the gland." .
