<http://human.owl#genid1446> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Small Cardiac Vein" .
<http://human.owl#genid1445> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Alimentary Canal" .
<http://human.owl#genid1444> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Digestive Tract" .
<http://human.owl#genid303> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Recto-Vesical Pouch" .
