<http://human.owl#genid50> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Large subcortical nuclear masses derived from the telencephalon and located in the basal regions of the cerebral hemispheres. (MeSH)" .
<http://human.owl#genid6708> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Nerve Cells" .
