<http://human.owl#genid1293> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The terminal portion of the gastrointestinal tract, extending from the rectosigmoid junction to the anal canal." .
<http://human.owl#genid1296> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The portion of the dental pulp cavity in the root of a tooth, extending from the pulp chamber to the apical foramen. More than one canal may be present in a single root." .
