<http://human.owl#genid1272> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The supporting and anchoring strand of connective tissue radiating out from the capsule through the interior of the lymph node." .
<http://human.owl#genid7164> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A flat, scale-like epithelial cell that forms the inner lining of the alveoli." .
<http://human.owl#genid1273> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Labyrinth" .
<http://human.owl#genid1274> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Internal Ear" .
