<http://human.owl#genid7149> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The main substance of the muscular wall of the heart enclosed between the epicardium and endocardium and composed of striated, involuntary cardiac muscle. (MeSH)" .
<http://human.owl#genid4441> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Endocervical Mucosa" .
<http://human.owl#genid3395> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "BFU-E - Burst-forming unit erythroid" .
<http://human.owl#genid7148> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sternum" .
