<http://human.owl#genid7159> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Any of the 12 paired nerves that originate in the brain stem." .
<http://human.owl#genid3389> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Interatrial Septum" .
<http://human.owl#genid4433> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Medium Pyramidal Cell Layer" .
<http://human.owl#genid4432> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Outer Pyramidal Cell Layer" .
<http://human.owl#genid3377> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lower-inner Quadrant of Breast" .
<http://human.owl#genid3376> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Tissue composed of neuroepithelial cells. The latter include astrocytes, oligodendrocytes, ependymal cells, neuroblasts, and olfactory receptor cells." .
<http://human.owl#genid3379> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The quarter of the breast which is inferior and medial." .
