<http://human.owl#genid1852> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Posterior Circumflex Artery" .
<http://human.owl#genid1853> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Two-layered muscularis mucosa extending into the small intestinal villi, where the smooth muscle cells form a longitudinal bundle in the centre of the villi. It is located between the lamina propria and submucosa of the small intestine." .
