<http://human.owl#genid6185> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A transparent homogeneous acellular layer, 6 to 9 um thick, lying between the basal lamina of the outer layer of stratified epithelium and the substantia propria of the cornea; it is considered to be a basement membrane." .
<http://human.owl#genid5361> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Vein of Galen" .
<http://human.owl#genid6813> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Corneal Endothelium" .
<http://human.owl#genid6815> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Neurons, Fusimotor" .
<http://human.owl#genid6814> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Motor neurons which activate the contractile regions of intrafusal muscle fibers, thus adjusting the sensitivity of the muscle spindles to stretch. (MeSH)" .
<http://human.owl#genid6817> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Motor Neurons, Gamma" .
<http://human.owl#genid6816> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Motor Neurons, Gamma-Efferent" .
<http://human.owl#genid6819> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Orifice of the Eustachian Tube" .
<http://human.owl#genid6818> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Gamma Motor Neuron" .
<http://human.owl#genid5377> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Body of the Lateral Ventricle" .
<http://human.owl#genid6178> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dentate Gyrus" .
<http://human.owl#genid6177> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Nasal Cavity" .
<http://human.owl#genid5375> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Cranial Nerve IX" .
<http://human.owl#genid5374> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Glossopharyngeal Nerve" .
<http://human.owl#genid6820> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Orifice of the Auditory Tube" .
<http://human.owl#genid5379> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dorsal Thoracic Artery" .
