<http://human.owl#genid6822> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Orifice of Auditory Tube" .
<http://human.owl#genid5378> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Thoracodorsal Artery" .
<http://human.owl#genid6170> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Subarachnoid Cistern" .
<http://human.owl#genid6172> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Endocrine Pancreas" .
<http://human.owl#genid5373> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Nervus Glossopharyngeus" .
<http://human.owl#genid5372> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ninth Cranial Nerve" .
<http://human.owl#genid6176> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "nasal cavity" .
<http://human.owl#genid5371> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "A membrane lining the external walls of the body cavities and reflected over the surfaces of protruding organs. It consists of mesothelium lying on a connective tissue layer, and secretes a watery exudate." .
<http://human.owl#genid6175> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The proximal portion of the respiratory passages on either side of the nasal septum, lined with ciliated mucosa, extending from the nares to the pharynx. (MeSH)" .
<http://human.owl#genid5370> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Serosa" .
